name: 1.2.11 Release
body:
## What's Changed
* Bug/event racing by @mondain in https://github.com/Red5/red5-server-common/pull/81

## New Contributors
* @mondain made their first contribution in https://github.com/Red5/red5-server-common/pull/81

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/Red5/red5-server-common/compare/v1.2.10...v1.2.11

Primarily a fix for the orderly ingest of RTMP into a direct consumer queue for each originating connection.
